body:
Don’t get me wrong I hope with all my heart and soul that Loki is alive but…

The argument that MARVEL has said Loki will play a vital part in defeating Thanos could not be as straight forward as you may think. I saw another theory talking about how Loki sacrificed himself because he knew Thanos wouldn’t kill Thor if one of them died (to keep it balanced). So Loki saving Thor who then went on to create Stormbreaker which will ultimately kill Thanos is his “vital part”. I hate to say it but maybe the major part Loki plays in defeating Thanos is by letting Thor live.
